Rex! It's time for a
fun drinking party!

rows.label: tlk0001027_msg0002
rows.name:
We still have a long way to go
before we reach our destination...

rows.label: tlk0001027_msg0003
rows.name:
Resting your body well to prepare
for the real thing is what makes
a first-class salvager.

rows.label: tlk0001027_msg0004
rows.name:
That may be true, but I was
asked to stand watch...

rows.label: tlk0001027_msg0005
rows.name:
Well, can't be helped then.
Go on and give it your all!

rows.label: tlk0001027_msg0006
rows.name:
They say you should buy hardship
when you're young! Hahaha!
